  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>How To Mine</h1>
  </div>
  <p class="lead">In order to mine on this pool you need to have an
    <a href="https://github.com/wiseplat/webthree-umbrella/releases" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">wshminer</a> installation
    pointed to<br/><code>{{config.HttpHost}}:{{config.HttpPort}}/YOUR_WSH_ADDRESS/RIG_ID</code>
  </p>
  <dl class="dl-horizontal">
    <dt>YOUR_WSH_ADDRESS</dt>
    <dd>This is your address for payouts, generate one with gwsh, or mine directly to exchange like
      <a href="http://poloniex.com" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Poloniex</a>
      or <a href="http://bittrex.com" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Bittrex</a>.<br/>
      <strong>Example:</strong> <code>0xc285f9dc21232fe887830234631adb9544e40d31</code>.
    </dd>
    <dt>RIG_ID</dt>
    <dd>
      ID of your farm to distinguish it from your other rig. If you have just one rig, feel free to omit this param.
      This param must be short alphanumeric string with optional dashes and underscores.<br/>
      <strong>Example:</strong> <code>rig-1</code>
    </dd>
  </dl>
  <p>
    <strong>Full example:</strong>
    <code>wshminer -F {{config.HttpHost}}:{{config.HttpPort}}/0xc285f9dc21232fe887830234631adb9544e40d31/myfarm -G --farm-recheck 200</code>.<br/>
    <span class="label label-info">Hint:</span> If you are compiling wshminer from latest source, please also use
      extra <code>--disable-submit-hashrate</code> option.
  </p>

  <h4>Stratum Mining with Stratum Proxy for Wiseplat</h4>
  <p class="lead">Grab proxy from <a href="https://github.com/wiseplat/wsh-proxy" re="nofollow" target="_blank">wsh-proxy GitHub repo</a>.</p>
  <p class="lead">Edit <code>wsh-proxy.conf</code> and specify our pool's <code>HOST: {{config.StratumHost}}</code>, <code>PORT: {{config.StratumPort}}</code> and your <code>WALLET</code>.</p>

  <h4>Mining with Wise-Proxy</h4>
  <p class="lead">Use stable release of <a href="https://github.com/wiseplat/wise-proxy/releases" target="_blank">Wiseplat Solo/Pool Mining Proxy</a>.</p>

